[SN]TITLE[SN]
Get Inspired: Learn four amazing basketball tricks from the Harlem Globetrotters!

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Harlem Globetrotters star Firefly lights up the court with his fantastic basketball tricks. He has created a four part tutorial exclusively for Get Inspired to teach you how he uses these tricks during the game.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
